org.danja.feedreader.parsers

Class SoupParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.danja.feedreader.parsers.SoupParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FeedParser, org.xml.sax.ContentHandler

    public class SoupParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements FeedParser, org.xml.sax.ContentHandler
    Tag soup/ill-formed HTML/XML parser produces SAX2 callbacks mostly namespace-aware (can't handle nested default namespaces) fairly direct port from Python version: http://dannyayers.com/archives/2004/07/11/tag-soup-play-code/
